We do have a video coming out the day after Aus Day (we always upload on Saturday morning Aus time) and it will be centered around cricket and the BBL. Just editing it now, it's an absolute ripper! Hilarious!

We're so grateful to have the chance to go on such an epic adventure and set a ripper new world record. We never dreamed that we'd accomplish anything like this when we started making trick shots back in 2009 in our backyards. A big thanks to everyone who gets behind us by watching our videos, especially those legends in the #44Club who stay 'til the very end, you're awesome! 
We will put out lots more content from our trip including an extended video of the shot that tells a more detailed story and includes a commtest so stay tuned for that next month. If you enjoyed this vid make sure you give it a like and if you want to get on board and subscribe that'd be great! Cheers!
